{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1024,"text":"Growing up in Kenya,"},{"time":2890,"text":"I knew I always wanted\nto study biochemistry."},{"time":7088,"text":"See, I had seen the impact of the high\nprevalence of diseases like malaria,"},{"time":12643,"text":"and I wanted to make medicines\nthat would cure the sick."},{"time":15765,"text":"So I worked really hard,"},{"time":17174,"text":"got a scholarship to the United States,\nwhere I became a cancer researcher,"},{"time":20985,"text":"and I loved it."},{"time":22612,"text":"For someone who wants to cure diseases,"},{"time":24723,"text":"there is no higher calling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27321,"text":"Ten years later, I returned\nto Kenya to do just that."},{"time":31201,"text":"A freshly minted PhD,"},{"time":33186,"text":"ready to take on this horrific illness,"},{"time":35411,"text":"which in Kenya was almost\ncertainly a death sentence."},{"time":39601,"text":"But instead of landing a job\nin a pharmaceutical company"},{"time":42576,"text":"or a hospital,"},{"time":44489,"text":"I found myself drawn\nto a different kind of lab,"},{"time":47366,"text":"working with a different\nkind of patient --"},{"time":49766,"text":"a patient whose illness was so serious"},{"time":52144,"text":"it impacted every single\nperson in my country;"},{"time":55618,"text":"a patient who needed to get healthy fast."},{"time":58328,"text":"That patient was my government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62126,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64102,"text":"See, many of us will agree that lots\nof governments are unhealthy today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68876,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":70983,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":76814,"text":"And Kenya was no exception."},{"time":78975,"text":"When I returned to Kenya in 2014,"},{"time":81502,"text":"there was 17 percent youth unemployment."},{"time":84785,"text":"And Nairobi, the major business hub,"},{"time":87157,"text":"was rated 177th on the quality\nof living index."},{"time":91256,"text":"It was bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94270,"text":"Now, an economy is only as healthy\nas the entities that make it up."},{"time":99187,"text":"So when government --"},{"time":100361,"text":"one of its most vital entities --"},{"time":102130,"text":"is weak or unhealthy,"},{"time":103592,"text":"everyone and everything suffers."},{"time":106522,"text":"Sometimes you might\nput a Band-Aid in place"},{"time":109319,"text":"to try and temporarily stop the pain."},{"time":112732,"text":"Maybe some of you here have participated"},{"time":114738,"text":"in a Band-Aid operation\nto an African country --"},{"time":117741,"text":"setting up alternative schools,\nbuilding hospitals, digging wells --"},{"time":122247,"text":"because governments there\neither weren't or couldn't provide"},{"time":125208,"text":"the services to their citizens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127900,"text":"We all know this is a temporary solution."},{"time":131455,"text":"There are just some things\nBand-Aids can't fix,"},{"time":135027,"text":"like providing an environment\nwhere businesses feel secure"},{"time":139440,"text":"that they'll have an equal opportunity"},{"time":141275,"text":"to be able to run and start\ntheir businesses successfully."},{"time":144541,"text":"Or there are systems in place"},{"time":146379,"text":"that would protect the private\nproperty that they create."},{"time":149444,"text":"I would argue,"},{"time":150625,"text":"only government is capable of creating\nthese necessary conditions"},{"time":154093,"text":"for economies to thrive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":156549,"text":"Economies thrive when business are able\nto quickly and easily set up shop."},{"time":161411,"text":"Business owners create new sources\nof income for themselves,"},{"time":164807,"text":"new jobs get added into the economy"},{"time":167282,"text":"and then more taxes are paid\nto fund public projects."},{"time":171504,"text":"New business is good for everyone."},{"time":174415,"text":"And it's such an important measure\nof economic growth,"},{"time":177269,"text":"the World Bank has a ranking called\nthe \"Ease of Doing Business Ranking,\""},{"time":181244,"text":"which measures how easy\nor difficult it is to start a business"},{"time":184305,"text":"in any given country."},{"time":185926,"text":"And as you can imagine,"},{"time":188404,"text":"starting or running a business\nin a country with an ailing government --"},{"time":192049,"text":"almost impossible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194432,"text":"The President of Kenya knew this,\nwhich is why in 2014,"},{"time":198180,"text":"he came to our lab and asked\nus to partner with him"},{"time":201573,"text":"to be able to help Kenya\nto jump-start business growth."},{"time":205689,"text":"He set an ambitious goal:"},{"time":207778,"text":"he wanted Kenya to be ranked top 50\nin this World Bank ranking."},{"time":213167,"text":"In 2014 when he came,"},{"time":215268,"text":"Kenya was ranked 136 out of 189 countries."},{"time":220071,"text":"We had our work cut out for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223592,"text":"Fortunately, he came to the right place."},{"time":226317,"text":"We're not just a Band-Aid kind of team."},{"time":228668,"text":"We're a group of computer scientists,\nmathematicians, engineers"},{"time":232458,"text":"and a cancer researcher,"},{"time":234419,"text":"who understood that in order\nto cure the sickness"},{"time":236889,"text":"of a system as big as government,"},{"time":238987,"text":"we needed to examine the whole body,"},{"time":241411,"text":"and then we needed to drill down\nall the way from the organs,"},{"time":244522,"text":"into the tissues,"},{"time":245879,"text":"all the way to single cells,"},{"time":247405,"text":"so that we could properly\nmake a diagnosis."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250762,"text":"So with our marching orders\nfrom the President himself,"},{"time":253617,"text":"we embarked on the purest\nof the scientific method:"},{"time":256754,"text":"collecting data --"},{"time":257953,"text":"all the data we could get our hands on --"},{"time":260064,"text":"making hypotheses,"},{"time":261345,"text":"creating solutions,"},{"time":262606,"text":"one after the other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264845,"text":"So we met with hundreds of individuals\nwho worked at government agencies,"},{"time":268904,"text":"from the tax agency, the lands\noffice, utilities company,"},{"time":272864,"text":"the agency that's responsible\nfor registering companies,"},{"time":276356,"text":"and with each of them, we observed\nthem as they served customers,"},{"time":279979,"text":"we documented their processes --\nmost of them were manual."},{"time":285473,"text":"We also just went back and looked at\na lot of their previous paperwork"},{"time":288953,"text":"to try and really understand;"},{"time":291145,"text":"to try and diagnose what bodily\nmalfunctions had occurred"},{"time":294519,"text":"that lead to that 136th spot\non the World Bank list."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298248,"text":"What did we find?"},{"time":299974,"text":"Well, in Kenya it was taking 72 days"},{"time":304069,"text":"for a business owner\nto register their property,"},{"time":307037,"text":"compared to just one day in New Zealand,"},{"time":309458,"text":"which was ranked second\non the World Bank list."},{"time":312827,"text":"It took 158 days to get\na new electric connection."},{"time":317879,"text":"In Korea it took 18 days."},{"time":320984,"text":"If you wanted to get a construction permit"},{"time":323061,"text":"so you could put up a building,"},{"time":324605,"text":"in Kenya, it was going\nto take you 125 days."},{"time":328200,"text":"In Singapore, which is ranked first,\nthat would only take you 26 days."},{"time":333580,"text":"God forbid you had to go to court"},{"time":335648,"text":"to get help in being able to settle\na dispute to enforce a contract,"},{"time":339559,"text":"because that process alone\nwould take you 465 days."},{"time":345065,"text":"And if that wasn't bad enough,"},{"time":348675,"text":"you would lose 40 percent\nof your claim in just fees --"},{"time":352851,"text":"legal fees, enforcement fees, court fees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":357108,"text":"Now, I know what you're thinking:"},{"time":360726,"text":"for there to exist such inefficiencies\nin an African country,"},{"time":364417,"text":"there must be corruption."},{"time":366491,"text":"The very cells that run the show\nmust be corrupt to the bone."},{"time":370972,"text":"I thought so, too, actually."},{"time":372984,"text":"When we started out,"},{"time":374161,"text":"I thought I was going to find\nso much corruption,"},{"time":377673,"text":"I was literally going to either die\nor get killed in the process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381193,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":384946,"text":"But when we dug deeper,"},{"time":386925,"text":"we didn't find corruption\nin the classic sense:"},{"time":390106,"text":"slimy gangsters lurking in the darkness,"},{"time":393138,"text":"waiting to grease the palms\nof their friends."},{"time":396139,"text":"What we found was an overwhelming\nsense of helplessness."},{"time":401684,"text":"Our government was sick,"},{"time":402970,"text":"because government\nemployees felt helpless."},{"time":406993,"text":"They felt that they were not\nempowered to drive change."},{"time":410600,"text":"And when people feel stuck and helpless,"},{"time":414968,"text":"they stop seeing their role\nin a bigger system."},{"time":418265,"text":"They start to think the work they do\ndoesn't matter in driving change."},{"time":422758,"text":"And when that happens,"},{"time":424588,"text":"things slow down,"},{"time":426205,"text":"fall through the cracks"},{"time":427649,"text":"and inefficiencies flourish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":431171,"text":"Now imagine with me,"},{"time":432960,"text":"if you had a process\nyou had to go through --"},{"time":436922,"text":"had no other alternative --"},{"time":438716,"text":"and this process was inefficient, complex"},{"time":442461,"text":"and very, very slow."},{"time":443875,"text":"What would you do?"},{"time":446482,"text":"I think you might start by trying\nto find somebody to outsource it to,"},{"time":449834,"text":"so that they can just\ntake care of that for you."},{"time":452800,"text":"If that doesn't work,"},{"time":455307,"text":"maybe you'd consider paying somebody"},{"time":457341,"text":"to just \"unofficially\" take care\nof it on your behalf --"},{"time":460745,"text":"especially if you thought\nnobody was going to catch you."},{"time":464790,"text":"Not out of malice or greed,"},{"time":467184,"text":"just trying to make sure that you get\nsomething to work for you"},{"time":470299,"text":"so you can move on."},{"time":471918,"text":"Unfortunately, that\nis the beginning of corruption."},{"time":475439,"text":"And if left to thrive and grow,"},{"time":477786,"text":"it seeps into the whole system,"},{"time":479376,"text":"and before you know it,"},{"time":480770,"text":"the whole body is sick."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484596,"text":"Knowing this,"},{"time":485913,"text":"we had to start by making sure"},{"time":487492,"text":"that every single stakeholder\nwe worked with had a shared vision"},{"time":492093,"text":"for what we wanted to do."},{"time":494192,"text":"So we met with everyone,"},{"time":496656,"text":"from the clerk whose sole job\nis to remove staples"},{"time":499239,"text":"from application packets,"},{"time":501446,"text":"to the legal drafters\nat the attorney general's office,"},{"time":505187,"text":"to the clerks who are responsible\nfor serving business owners"},{"time":508208,"text":"when they came to access\ngovernment services."},{"time":511557,"text":"And with them,"},{"time":512731,"text":"we made sure that they understood"},{"time":514327,"text":"how their day-to-day actions\nwere impacting our ability as a country"},{"time":519098,"text":"to create new jobs\nand to attract investments."},{"time":522605,"text":"No one's role was too small;\neveryone's role was vital."}]},{"cues":[{"time":528087,"text":"Now, guess what we started to see?"},{"time":530994,"text":"A coalition of government employees"},{"time":533031,"text":"who are excited and ready to drive change,"},{"time":535167,"text":"began to grow and form."},{"time":537927,"text":"And together we started\nto implement changes"},{"time":540555,"text":"that impacted the service\ndelivery of our country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544585,"text":"The result?"},{"time":546033,"text":"In just two years,"},{"time":548098,"text":"Kenya's ranking moved from 136 to 92."}]},{"cues":[{"time":553024,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":560520,"text":"And in recognition of the significant\nreforms we've been able to implement"},{"time":564933,"text":"in such a short time,"},{"time":566736,"text":"Kenya was recognized"},{"time":568641,"text":"to be among the top three\nglobal reformers in the world"},{"time":572251,"text":"two years in a row."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574698,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":581164,"text":"Are we fully healthy?"},{"time":583556,"text":"No."},{"time":585149,"text":"We have some serious work still to do."},{"time":588336,"text":"I like to think about these two years\nlike a weight-loss program."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592175,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":594521,"text":"It's that time after months\nof hard, grueling work at the gym,"},{"time":598507,"text":"and then you get your first\ntime to weigh yourself,"},{"time":600961,"text":"and you've lost 20 pounds."},{"time":603007,"text":"You're feeling unstoppable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":606697,"text":"Now, some of you may think\nthis doesn't apply to you."},{"time":611058,"text":"You're not from Kenya."},{"time":612432,"text":"You don't intend to be an entrepreneur."},{"time":614598,"text":"But think with me for just a moment."},{"time":617314,"text":"When is the last time\nyou accessed a government service?"},{"time":621980,"text":"Maybe applied for your driver's license,"},{"time":624780,"text":"tried to do your taxes on your own."},{"time":630644,"text":"It's easy in this political\nand global economy"},{"time":633438,"text":"to want to give up when we think\nabout transforming government."},{"time":637386,"text":"We can easily resign to the fact\nor to the thinking"},{"time":640911,"text":"that government is too inefficient,"},{"time":643277,"text":"too corrupt,"},{"time":644457,"text":"unfixable."},{"time":646527,"text":"We might even rarely get\nsome key government responsibilities"},{"time":649988,"text":"to other sectors,"},{"time":651212,"text":"to Band-Aid solutions,"},{"time":652405,"text":"or to just give up and feel helpless."},{"time":656029,"text":"But just because a system is sick\ndoesn't mean it's dying."},{"time":660689,"text":"We cannot afford to give up"},{"time":663520,"text":"when it comes to the challenges\nof fixing our governments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667989,"text":"In the end,"},{"time":670682,"text":"what really makes a government healthy\nis when healthy cells --"},{"time":674881,"text":"that's you and I --"},{"time":677834,"text":"get to the ground,"},{"time":679505,"text":"roll up our sleeves,"},{"time":680813,"text":"refuse to be helpless"},{"time":682942,"text":"and believe that sometimes,"},{"time":684762,"text":"all it takes is for us\nto create some space"},{"time":688016,"text":"for healthy cells to grow and thrive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":690781,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691962,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}